 497:libraries/drivers/src/at32f403a_407_can.c **** /**
 498:libraries/drivers/src/at32f403a_407_can.c ****   * @brief  check the transmission state of the specified can peripheral.
 499:libraries/drivers/src/at32f403a_407_can.c ****   * @param  can_x: select the can peripheral.
 500:libraries/drivers/src/at32f403a_407_can.c ****   *         this parameter can be one of the following values:
 501:libraries/drivers/src/at32f403a_407_can.c ****   *         CAN1 or CAN2.
 502:libraries/drivers/src/at32f403a_407_can.c ****   * @param  transmit_mailbox: the number of the mailbox that is used for transmission.
 503:libraries/drivers/src/at32f403a_407_can.c ****   *         this parameter can be one of the following values:
 504:libraries/drivers/src/at32f403a_407_can.c ****   *         - CAN_TX_MAILBOX0
 505:libraries/drivers/src/at32f403a_407_can.c ****   *         - CAN_TX_MAILBOX1
 506:libraries/drivers/src/at32f403a_407_can.c ****   *         - CAN_TX_MAILBOX2
